-- Agricultural Bank's Pan Says No Fund-Raising for Three Years, HKET Reports
-- Mark Lee
-- 2010-07-17T06:16:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-17/agricultural-bank-s-pan-says-no-fund-raising-for-three-years-hket-reports.html

          
          
             Agricultural Bank of China Ltd. has
no plan to raise more capital in the next two to three years,
Hong Kong Economic Times reported, citing Vice President Pan
Gongsheng. The Chinese lender can replenish capital from
retained profit, the Hong Kong-based newspaper cited Pan as
saying in an interview.  
